items.name: HameFMix2
items.description:
The English explanation is after the Japanese!

ノイズを抑えるため、CFGScaleFixの利用を強く推奨します（前のモデルと違い、必須ではありません）HighlyNoiseモデルは必須です

To reduce noise, CFGScaleFix is strongly recommended (unlike the previous model, it is not mandatory)　HighlyNoise-model is a must

CFGScaleFixを使用しない場合は、CFGを7±2に設定してください

If CFGScaleFix is not used, set CFG to 7±2

CFGScaleFixの設定は下の画像をご覧ください（1例です）

See the image below for a setting (one example).　CFG=20~30

主に色調に問題があったHameFMixの改良版です。また、色調だけでなく、ベースモデルがMeinaHentaiV4からHassakuV1.3に変わっています。つまるところ1girlのみで出力すると薄着の女の子が出てきます。

HameFMixは、馬鹿な私がブルーライトカットメガネを掛けたまま色調を調整したので、すごく青色が強いモデルになっていました。今回はクリアカラーメガネを調達したので、色の問題は解決していると思います。（反動で少し明るすぎるかも）

その他の変更点としては、Hassakuの比率を大幅に増やしたことと、VAE無しでもそこそこきれいなイラストが出力できるようになったことです。それでも、VAE無しだと少しだけイラストが滲んでしまい、低解像度で出力するとよくわからない画像が出てきます。必要でに応じて色調に大きな影響を与えないClearVAE_V2.3やClean_VAEなどを使用してください。

以下各モデルの説明

Aモデル

  • CFGScaleFixがなくてもきれいなイラストが出力できるように調節したモデルです。

  • かわりに背景や服の書き込みは少し弱めです。

Bモデル

  • ノイズを強めにいれたモデルです。

  • 情報量は多くなりますが、見にくい生成物も多くなります

Cモデル

  • 出力画像を暗めに調整しコントラストをはっきりとさせた私好みのモデルです。

Dモデル

  • BとCを組み合わせたモデルです。

  • 情報量は非常に多いですが、その分構図の破綻が増えます。

Eモデル

  • 旧HameFMixと同じく、CFGScaleFixを必須とするモデルです。

  • これがないと生成画像が歪みます。

21モデル

  • 少しだけ旧HameFMixに戻しました

  • 性能はよくわかりません

25モデル

  • LoRAなどマージして更に調整を行いました

  • M00を完全にMeinaHentaiV4と同じものに置き換えました。これにより、MeinaHentaiV4と同じプロンプト入力で生成できます

  • Aはノイズを最適化し、HighlyNoiseは限界ギリギリまでノイズを強めています。

既知の問題点

  • 手を改善しようと頑張ったら、正確性は上がったけど手がデカくなった。

    →BadHandNegative等を使用して補正してください。申し訳ない。

  • NSFWイラストを出そうとすると手足がおかしくなる。

    →Meinaがベースだった前作と異なりhassakuがベースのこのモデルは細かい体位まで指定しないと手足がおかしくなりやすいです。また、SD1.5の限界で一辺が768を超えると崩壊しやすくなるので、16:9の画像は一度768x432で作ってから、アップスケーリングしてください。

English Description（deepL）

This is an improved version of HameFMix, which mainly had color tone problems. In addition to color tone, the base model has been changed from MeinaHentaiV4 to HassakuV1.3. The output with only 1girl at the end of the day will show a girl in light clothing.

HameFMix had a very blue model because I was stupid enough to adjust the color tone while wearing blue light cut glasses. This time I procured clear color glasses, so I think the color problem is solved. (maybe a little too bright in reaction)

Other changes include a significant increase in the ratio of Hassaku and the ability to output a reasonably clean illustration without VAE. Nevertheless, without VAE, the illustration will be slightly blurred, and output at low resolution will produce an image that is not well defined. If necessary, use ClearVAE_V2.3 or Clean_VAE, which do not affect the color tone significantly.

Description of each model below

A model

  • This model is adjusted to output beautiful illustrations without CFGScaleFix.

  • Instead, the background and clothing writing is a bit weaker.

B model

  • This model has a high noise level.

  • More information, but also more difficult-to-view products

C model

  • This model is my favorite, with the output image adjusted to be darker and the contrast clearer.

D model

  • This model combines B and C.

  • The amount of information is very large, but this increases the number of compositional breakdowns.

E model

  • Like the former HameFMix, this model requires CFGScaleFix.

  • Without it, the generated image will be distorted.

21 model

  • I reverted back to the old HameFMix for a bit.

  • Not sure about performance.

25 models

  • Further adjustments were made by merging LoRA, etc.

  • M00 was completely replaced with the same one as MeinaHentaiV4. This allows the same prompt input to be generated as in MeinaHentaiV4

  • A optimizes noise, while HighlyNoise intensifies noise to the very limit.

Known Issues

  • When I tried hard to improve the hands, my accuracy improved, but the hands got bigger.

    → Please use BadHandNegative or similar to compensate. Sorry.

  • When I try to produce NSFW illustrations, my limbs go haywire.

    →Unlike the previous model, which was based on Meina, this model, which is based on hassaku, is prone to limb errors unless even detailed body positions are specified. Also, since the model tends to collapse when one side exceeds 768 due to the limitation of SD1.5, please make a 16:9 image at 768x432 and then upscale it.

items.name: FoolKat GOD-OF-MONOCHROME
items.description:
Update 8/16/23 - Version 3 is out and it is far more versatile than the previous 2. It isn't locked into a specific art style and can do objects, animals, and landscapes now. Unlike the other versions, it does require trigger words. Without them, the images tend to be colored, so you can get interesting results without them.

Update 8/15/23 - A user made me aware of an issue that is happening in the model. I wasn't aware that the model is turning non-human prompts into women or adding them into the prompts. Version 1 doesn't do it as often, but they both have the issue. As such, I'm working on a version 3 that should do objects, landscapes, and more without adding women into the prompt or turning the prompt into a woman. Should be out soon.

Update 8/10/23 - Version 2 is out. V2 is the pruned version of V1. However, after pruning, the model had its monochromatic nature removed so I had to reapply the loras to the model merge, creating V2. The art style is slightly different and the model has a little more trouble creating monochromatic art than V1. As such, while they aren't required, I recommend adding tags like: monochromatic, coloring page, b&w, line art, etc.

This is the twentieth model in my GOD-OF series. I wasn't going to make any more of these models for a while, since I've been working on an SDXL model fine-tuning, but my PC isn't powerful enough so I'm probably going to have to buy VRAM from a place like runpod. In the meantime, to combat my frustration at things not going well with that model, I made this!

You can find all the models at GOD-OF-GREED, GOD-OF-ENVY, GOD-OF-LOVE, GOD-OF-ANIME, GOD-OF-LUST, GOD-OF-JUSTICE, GOD-OF-TIME, GOD-OF-FANTASY, GOD-OF-JOY, GOD-OF-HORROR, GOD-OF-PRIDE, GOD-OF-PUNK, GOD-OF-STORMS, GOD-OF-EUPHORIA, GOD-OF-GLUTTONY, GOD-OF-THE-WEST, GOD-OF-BEAUTY, GOD-OF-SEDUCTION, and GOD-OF-PEACE.

This model was created from one of my existing GOD-OF beta models, which won't be released to the public, merged with a few different lora for creating monochrome, line art, and sketch style images.

The model makes monochromatic art without having to use trigger words but will occasionally add hints of color here and there. The model also has a more difficult time making monochromatic images of male subjects. If you are having trouble getting the results you want, try adding one or more of these prompts: monochrome, line art, sketch, and coloring page. This tends to help.

The model has Blessed2 VAE baked into it, so no VAE required.

All of the images I upload for this model are unedited and don't use any special extensions like ControlNet. I do not do any inpainting or img2img to correct errors. Why? Because you deserve to see how the model works without any touchup or special extensions like ControlNet. You can surely get better images by putting in the extra work, which I do for my personal images. The samples are just meant to showcase what the model can do raw with nothing but prompt engineering.

items.name: Kōhei Horikoshi's Sketchbook
items.description:
A lora trained on Kōhei Horikoshi and their many works in order to evoke their style. while i cannot claim that this lora can produce every character that horikoshi may have illustrated, it may do a decent job for those that are widely represented in his sketches. This dataset isnt limited to just monochrome sketches, so feel free to shop around with prompts, though monochrome sketches do dominate the dataset.

I may, at a future date, try to train out the Japanese text that exists in a decent amount of the dataset and will show up unprompted in v1 all the time. I cannot claim that i will be successful in this endeavor so manage expectations accordingly.

items.name: Wuxiang Roll with Noodles/Wuxiang Mian(separated version)/闽南小吃五香面/豆干面份（单独版本）
items.description:
五香面（Wuxiang Mian）/豆干面份（Dougan Mianfen）

五香→Wuxiang Roll

豆干→thick fried bean curd

面份→a set of noodles

A kind of noodles in Zhangzhou, Fujian Province, China.

福建漳州的一种面。

If you eat it by grabbing it, it will be called 手抓面(Shouzhuamian, lit: hand grabbing noodles). As breakfast, what you should do is rolling Wuxiang Roll, thick fried bean curd or sausage with pre-steamed and pre-sauced Yellow alkaline noodles, then grabbing it and have a fast breakfast. Hand grabbing noodles was popular among harbor works. Sauce: Peanut Sesame (Peanut: Sesame = 9: 1), Satay Sauce, Sweet Chilli Sauce, Sweet Garlic Chili Sauce, Sweet Flour Paste.

您要是用手抓来吃它，那它叫手抓面。作为早餐，您需要做的就是用事先蒸好刷酱的碱水面卷上五香、豆干或者香肠然后享用一道快速的早餐。手抓面曾经在码头工人间受欢迎。酱是花生芝麻（9：1）酱、沙茶酱、甜辣酱、甜蒜蓉辣酱、甜面酱。

In restaurant, the noodles, wuxiang rolls, thick fried bean curd, fried pork and so on were cut into pieces(切面,Qiemian, lit: cut noodles). You can eat it with chopsticks or fork. Sauce: mix Peanut Sesame Sauce with sugar, water, minced onion. Usually, a bowl of Zhangpu meat ball soup or pig small intestine soup will be added in the order.

在馆子，面、五香、豆干、炸肉片等会被剪成小块（切面）。可以用筷子或者叉子食用。酱料是花生芝麻酱加糖水和洋葱碎。通常会加点漳浦肉丸汤或者猪小肠汤。

Dataset is mainly about Qiemian.

数据集主要和切面有关。

"wuxiangmian, holding, gloves, food" may generate Shouzhuamian.

"wuxiangmian, holding, gloves, food" 可能生成手抓面。

Your waifu may be influenced.

您二次元老婆可能会被影响。

If it is not enough, add "food".

如果不够，加入food

items.name: 【再世】next life-王天林
items.description:
这是群星再世第六十五期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

王天林，香港著名导演，监制，导演王晶的父亲，导演杜琪峰的师傅，1947年由叔父王鹏翼引领进入影视圈，先后做过冲印、录音、场记、助导等工作。1950年导演了首部电影作品《峨嵋飞剑侠》，之后开始一发不可收拾，经典电影无数，后来更是被称为香港“影坛教父”。

除了这些影视作品外，他也捧红和培育了很多优秀影视人才，1976年还是“排骨”的郑少秋就因为王天林的赏识才主演了经典电视剧《书剑恩仇录》，也因此剧，郑少秋一炮而红，后面《楚留香》也是王天林的作品。跟郑少秋情况类似的还有汪明荃，汪明荃的前期三部作品《书剑恩仇录》《京华春梦》《万水千山总是情》都是出自王天林之手。

王天林是开启TVB黄金时代的影坛教父，一辈子爱惜羽毛，在嗜赌如命欠下一屁股债的老婆面前，他也没有动过要接商业片的心思。虽然战功累累，但王天林并不快乐，经常深夜痛哭，在艺术和商业之间苦苦挣扎。

2010年，王天林因病去世，享年83岁。

items.name: Anis (Sparkling Summer) (NIKKE)
items.description:
Introduction

A LoRA model for new outfit of Anis called Sparkling Summer. The trigger tag is 'sparkling-anis'. The key features are 'swimsuit, bikini, eyewear on head, brown hair, medium hair, ahoge, sunglasses, open jacket, yellow jacket'. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version, 2.0 version Yesmix and MeinaMix to verify the compatibility of this LoRA model on different base models.

The preview images are generated using HiresFix+4xAnimeSharp that can be used by downloading .pth file and putting in the 'ESRGAN' folder.

Cautions (Must Read)

For anime model,

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

BTW, make sure set this option in 'Stable Diffusion' settings to 'CPU' to successfully regenerate the preview images with the same seed.

  • The training resolution of this model is 1024x1024, so generating resolution must not exceed this range. Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Io(Granblue Fantasy)/イオ
items.description:
Who?: Io is the main character wizard in Granblue Fantasy.

Weight: 0.8～1.0

Trigger:

  • Normal outfit : The study is a mixture of SR outfit and a new standing outfit, which lacks uniformity.

ioeuclase, hair ornament, white dress, black thighhighs, detached sleeves

  • Summer outfit :

iosummer, hair flower, frilled bikini

Although the hair may be missing, adding twintails stabilises the hair.

dark skin if necessary.

Issue:

  1. Low accuracy of official outfit due to priority given to switching backgrounds and costumes.

  2. In summer outfit, Sometimes hair ornament of normal outfit grows.

    Putting hair ornament in Negative could make it better.

  3. In summer outfit, Sometimes bikini frills grow on the arms.Why...?

  4. In summer outfit, The sea is summoned in the background.

    reduce the intensity of the lora or emphasise the background prompts.

digression:

SSRoutfit gives up after considering the lack of material and the impact on other outfits.

There is too much of a swimming costume problem.

items.name: Aerial Simulation | Virtual Aerial Camera
items.description:
The purpose of model making is to simulate the simulation of aerial natural scenery shots. Personally, I currently think that the best matching base model is: (Crystal-Clear2_Crystal-Clear2), at least the model that is more realistic. Weights I mostly run at 0.8-1. I think the effect is not bad, at least it is more interesting than the aerial view of the single-hanging base model, although it is difficult to achieve the details, at least it can reach the level of mini2?

To generate suggestions, you can use the main trigger word "aerial photography" (the scenery of the lottery is still interesting), you can use "gradient_sky" to make the sky more beautiful and reasonable, "city" can come out more like a green city, and "snow" Landscape words such as "mountain", "ocean" and "cloud" can be effectively controlled, and "ice rock" can trigger an effect similar to a blue ice cave.

In fact, the idea of this model comes from my own aerial photos (mainly taken with mini3p), plus the works of some big guys in Sky City for training.
